 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Thick-fat:

    This Pokémon takes half as 
  much damage from fire- and ice-type 
  moves.

  Own-tempo:

    This Pokémon cannot be confused.

  If a Pokémon is confused and 
  acquires this ability, its confusion 
  will immediately be healed.

  Defiant:

    When any of this Pokémon's 
  stats are lowered, its Attack 
  rises by two stages.

  If multiple stats are lowered 
  at once, this ability takes effect 
  with each stat lowered.


